I 'm doing this for you
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Ye</ENAMEX> has worked hard for <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">many years</ENAMEX> for the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Taiwanese</ENAMEX> community in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Dongguan</ENAMEX> , a subject he cares deeply about .
" I do n't care if it 's nothing more than a thatched - roof cottage ; I want to get a school for <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Taiwanese</ENAMEX> children up and running . "
