Teacher seniority was also a major issue in the effort to get the school established ; if teachers from public schools were to teach in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Dongguan</ENAMEX> , would they retain the seniority that they had built up in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> ?
