As for the appointment of a principal , <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">TBAD</ENAMEX> vice chairman <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Andrew Yeh</ENAMEX> states , " I think the mainland authorities will handle the situation flexibly .
