The <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Dongguan</ENAMEX> city government has leased an <ENAMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">86,000 - square - meter</ENAMEX> site to the association at an extremely low price , and the school 's cornerstone was laid <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">last year</ENAMEX> in a ceremony held on <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">3 November</ENAMEX> .
