According to <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Huang Su</ENAMEX> , executive director of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Little Oxford</ENAMEX> , " A lot of parents keep after me to make sure that the children 's education is exactly like the regular system in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> , but I have to remind them that once you 've left in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> , you 're not regular any longer . "
According to <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Huang</ENAMEX> , making the school a mirror image of those in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> does not necessarily mean that you are running a good school .
