In addition to <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Taiwanese</ENAMEX> teaching materials , she has also incorporated some materials from the mainland and overseas into the curriculum .
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Huang Su</ENAMEX> , who hails from <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Beijing</ENAMEX> , majored in <ENAMEX TYPE="LANGUAGE">English</ENAMEX> at university and is keenly interested in education .
