The <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Taiwanese</ENAMEX> kids at <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Little Oxford</ENAMEX> come from many different backgrounds .
Some speak in a mixture of <ENAMEX TYPE="LANGUAGE">Chinese</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="LANGUAGE">English</ENAMEX> , while others speak and look just like any mainland <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Chinese</ENAMEX> child .
